  },
  {
    "row": 61,
    "rowsha": "+nDdfkDsJNdaA463jSIH43SbZfChroGpWO7X+Ao8vfs=",
    "originContent": "  A simple file explorer that was born because I wanted to learn the Rust language.",
    "translatedContent": "  Rust言語を学びたいと思ったことから生まれたシンプルなファイルエクスプローラーです。"
  },
  {
    "row": 62,
    "rowsha": "9LaBX1pLj0uNH7jpkfGU+pcX+uzIPdfr4/tPIT1shWQ=",
    "originContent": "  <br>",
    "translatedContent": "  <br>"
  },
  {
    "row": 63,
    "rowsha": "XSUtC95yCw4IfsITzW7YOBxgqxc+17xtHwu26YOIEsE=",
    "originContent": "  It is operating system independent and trimmed for optimization.",
    "translatedContent": "  OSに依存せず、最適化のためにスリム化されています。"
  },
  {
    "row": 64,
    "rowsha": "dSdvPNAZSmR86FDDSF6tkQUCVfI9qmACHOR5tThOetY=",
    "originContent": "</p>",
    "translatedContent": "</p>"
  },
